INVESTIGATION OF,GUATEMALA~ @95@ PRESIDENT CLINTON HAS CALLED FOR A FULL REVIEW OF SEVERAL KILLINGS AND DISAPPEARANCE IN GUATEMALA THAT SOME HAVE CLAIMED WERE CARRIED OUT BY CIA AND WERE KNOWN BY OTHER FEDERAL AGENCIES. INTEL OVERSIGHT BOARD (IOB) TO CONDUCT REVIEW. NSC ADVISOR LAKE TO ADVISE ALL AGENCIES TO PRESERVE ANY RELATED DOCUMENTS. A NATIONAL SECURITY AGENCY ANONYMOUS EMPLOYEE CHARGED NSA MAY HAVE KNOWN OF MURDERS WHEN THEY OCCURED~ THAT THE ARMY ACTUALLY MAY HAVE BEEN INVOLVED AND THAT BOTH AGENCIES TRIED TO CONCEAL THEIR INVOLVEMERNT BY SHREDDING DOCUMENTS. FBI LOOKING INTO ALLEGATIONS. PENTAGON CONSULTANT~ SAMUEL BLAKE CHARGED CIA AND STATE DEPT KNEW MORE THAN THEY ADMITTED ABOUT THE DECADE-OLD MURDERS OF TWO OTHER AMERICANS ONE OF WHOM WAS BROTHER OF BLAKE. <WT 3/31/95 A4
INVESTIGATION OF,HAITI~ @87-93@ HOUSE AND SENATE INTEL COMMITTEES HAVE BEGUN PROBING CIA'S PAST TIES TO KEY HAITIAN POLITICAL AND MILITARY FIGURES~ INCLUDING COVERT PAYMENTS TO HAITIAN OFFICIALS FOR INFO ON LOCAL POLITICS. PROBES ARISE FROM ALLEGATIONS THAT UNFLATTERING CIA PROFILE MAY HAVE BEEN TAINTED BY CIA'S PAST ASSOCIATIONS WITH ARISTIDE'S OPPONENTS. REP. TORRICELLI (D-N.J.) SAID THERE WERE RELATIONSHIPS BETWEEN CIA AND SOME OF HAITI'S CURRENT LEADERSHIP. <WP 11/3/93 A16
INVESTIGATION OF,HIC AND INVESTIGATION OF ROLE OF CIA IN S&L CRISIS. <ITT 12/11/90 5
INVESTIGATION OF,HIC IN @90@ SAID IT COULD FIND NO SUPPORT FOR ALLEGATIONS THAT CIA WAS INVOLVED IN NATIONS SAVING AND LOANS SCANDALS (S&L). BEILENSON ANNOUNCED FINDING IN 2-PAGE LETTER TO BANKING SUBCOMMITTEE. FIVE INDIVIDUALS IDENTIFIED DURING INQUIRY DID HAVE ^AT SOME POINT IN THEIR LIVES^ AN ASSOCIATION WITH THE CIA BUT THERE NO EVIDENCE FOUND TO SHOW ASSOCIATIONS USED IN WAY TO FACILITATE FRADULENT ACTIVITIES AT FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS. HIC FOUND CIA HAD BEEN CONSUMER OF CERTAIN FINANCIAL SERVICES AT 4 INSTITUTIONS MENTIONED BY HOUSTON POST~ BUT THOSE RELATIONSHIPS CONSISTENT WITH ROUTINE AGENCY FINANCIAL PRACTICES. <WP 12/27/90 A4
